{"title":"海河行","authors":["朱光"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":8,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"海河行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"买舟消暑海河行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜得甘霖乍放晴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两岸青纱如浪涌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农忙铲趟杂歌声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芦荻菁菁傍水生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堤边柳伞绿相迎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村童放读溪头浴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊起一江白鹭鸣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渔舟唱晚趁新晴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"载得鱼归送入城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"物美价廉人尽喜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱家公社远传名。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江村处处晚烟轻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瓜豆门前结满棚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孺妇迎舟遥舞手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声声汽笛问清平。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}